                     <interp inst="t18471025-2390-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 pair of bellows, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18471025-name-645" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-645" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
